.modal-header
    | Draft Player
.modal-body
    .alert.alert-danger(ng-if='$ctrl.error') An unknown error occurred while drafting player. Please try again.
    div
        label Select Team:Â 
            select(ng-model='$ctrl.selectedTeam', ng-options='team as team.name for team in $ctrl.teams track by id', ng-disabled='$ctrl.loading')
.modal-footer
    button.btn.btn-warning(ng-disabled='$ctrl.loading', ng-click='$ctrl.cancel()') Cancel
    button.btn.btn-primary(ng-disabled='$ctrl.loading || $ctrl.selectedTeam === null', ng-click='$ctrl.submit()') Submit
